| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1869 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 687fe538-9bb1-5347-b9cf-1e8e977f84b2"
